Package org.divxdede.commons

Interface Summary
Disposable General interface describing objet that can be disposed.
Filter<E> Represent any filter rule that can accept or refuse an item.
Sizable General interface describing any container objects that can have a size semantics.
 

Class Summary
Arrays Utilities for manipulating arrays.
Condition This class describe a Condition that can be satisfied or not.
IOUtils Class tools providing convenience methods for closing streams or any disposable objects.
Objects Help class for manipulating general objects.
